articles.title: Don’t blame MKBHD for the fate of Humane AI and Fisker - TechCrunch
articles.description: Famed YouTuber Marques Brownlee makes a splash not for what he said about Humane's Ai Pin, but for how he said it.
articles.content: Humane AI raised more than $230 million before it even shipped a product. And when it finally released its Ai Pin — which costs $699 plus a $24 monthly subscription — pretty much every tech reviewer … [+6380 chars]
